![image.png](/uploads/fa6725add6bcd5e453e1a93a9d7bbcf2/image.png){width="201" height="134"}

Similarly, clicking a video channel in the settings icon doesn't close the channel list. So I'm forced to click elsewhere, but my first natural place to click is right outside the dialog on top of the video, which makes the video go full screen

![image.png](/uploads/1f5b5ba5476928df48754f9f30e56b98/image.png){width=315 height=140}

Is there supposed to be padding between the info icon and the channels?

![image.png](/uploads/1399422cd8b209372e7e5acaca746365/image.png){width="158" height="49"}

Or a padding between the channels and the volume icon?

